data.title: Mike Dunleavy Jr. | Match Game
data.meta_description: By Conrad Theodore | Posted 11.07.2013 Imagine earning a nice, big salary and months of vacation time but not being the least bit happy about your situation. That’s the feeling Mike Dunleavy, Jr. says he's experienced nearly every summer for the last decade. “You turn on the TV and you see a bunch of teams playing for a championship but you’re at home, sitting on the couch watching,” explains Dunleavy. “It can be depressing.”
